declare that they have no competing interests.</p>\n              \n                <h3 class=\"c-article__sub-heading\" id=\"FPar3\">Publisher\u2019s Note</h3>\n                <p>Springer Nature remains neutral with regard to jurisdictional claims in published maps and institutional affiliations.</p>\n              </div></div></section><section aria-labelledby=\"author-information\" data-title=\"Author information\"><div class=\"c-article-section\" id=\"author-information-section\"><h2 class=\"c-article-section__title js-section-title js-c-reading-companion-sections-item\" id=\"author-information\">Author information</h2><div class=\"c-article-section__content\" id=\"author-information-content\"><h3 class=\"c-article__sub-heading\" id=\"affiliations\">Affiliations</h3><ol class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__list\"><li id=\"Aff1\"><p class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__address\">Department of Business Information Systems, Leipzig University, Grimmaische Stra\u00dfe 12, 04109, Leipzig, Germany</p><p class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list\">Andr\u00e9 M\u00fcller\u00a0&amp;\u00a0Bogdan Franczyk</p></li><li id=\"Aff2\"><p class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__address\">K\u00fchne Logistics University, Gro\u00dfer Grasbrook 17, 20457, Hamburg, Germany</p><p class=\"c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list\">Andr\u00e9 Ludwig</p></li></ol><div class=\"u-js-hide u-hide-print\" data-test=\"author-info\"><span class=\"c-article__sub-heading\">Authors</span><ol class=\"c-article-authors-search u-list-reset\"><li id=\"auth-Andr_-M_ller\"><span class=\"c-article-authors-search__title u-h3 js-search-name\">Andr\u00e9 M\u00fcller</span><div class=\"c-article-authors-search__list\"><div class=\"c-article-authors-search__item c-article-authors-search__list-item--left\"><a href=\"/search?dc.creator=&#34;Andr%C3%A9+M%C3%BCller&#34;\" class=\"c-article-button\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"author link - publication\" data-track-label=\"link\">View auth